desc_content.paragraph: Soft body simulation settings for an object

list_item.paragraph: SIMPLE Simple, Edges receive a drag force from surrounding media.
LIFT_FORCE Lift Force, Edges receive a lift force when passing through surrounding media.

desc_content.paragraph: Absolute ball size or factor if not manually adjusted

list_item.paragraph: AVERAGE Average, Average Spring length * Ball Size.
MINIMAL Minimal, Minimal Spring length * Ball Size.
MAXIMAL Maximal, Maximal Spring length * Ball Size.
